com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.net

Class URLRequestHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.ProxyObject
      • com.emitrom.flash4j.core.client.net.URLRequestHeader

  • public class URLRequestHeader
extends ProxyObject
    A URLRequestHeader object encapsulates a single HTTP request header and consists of a name/value pair. URLRequestHeader objects are used in the requestHeaders property of the URLRequest class.
